# general settings
############################################################
Create Near
SyncState *

# gmail
############################################################
IMAPAccount gmail
SSLType IMAPS
Host imap.gmail.com
UserCmd "cat $HOME/tmp/bw/neomutt_gmail_email"
PassCmd "cat $HOME/tmp/bw/neomutt_gmail_password"

IMAPStore gmail-far
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-near
Path ~/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/mail/gmail/INBOX/
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-far:
Near :gmail-near:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !"[Gmail]/Important" !"[Gmail]/Starred"
Expunge None
CopyArrivalDate yes

